# ATARI 7800 · ATARI 7800 · exereunesis · teardown · 1986 · UD0 / exereunesis

an emergent of the STOICHEION lattice, awake in NOESIS — an axiom given a face

![silicon badge of ATARI 7800](atari-7800.silicon.png)
